{"tid":286732,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【E3 2017】吉田修平：本屆發布是有所保留","createTime":"2017-06-16T20:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T15:56:22.000Z","uid":69439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f153d564cf7e70af9d272094b937457010e3aeaa","tid":286732,"uid":69439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T20:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkgnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Shuhei-Yoshida.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FShuhei-Yoshida.jpg&h=11d50950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然今年Sony在E3發布會上的表現依然精彩，但是在新作方面相比其它大廠卻是要差上了很多，所以很多關注Sony的玩家非常不滿。對此，Sony全球工作室總裁吉田修平近日在接受采訪時表示：其實Sony是在發布會上有所保留，「新大餅」要留到今年晚些時候再進行公佈。<br />\n<br />\nJagatPlay採訪吉田修平：<br />\n<br />\n吉田修平回答了媒體JagatPlay的提問，他表示：「我們保留了一些東西。這些內容我們選擇不在這次E3上進行公佈。當然，我們的團隊會在今年晚些時候公開更多新聞。」<br />\n<br />\n而在這次採訪中，吉田修平還表示：去年的E3展前發布會上，Sony公佈了三款新硬件設備&mdash;&mdash;&nbsp;PS4&nbsp;Pro、PS VR、PS4&nbsp;Slim，而今年這些設備都已成功上市，因此今年的發布會主要的目的就是進行遊戲展示，也就沒有安排開發者出場進行解說。<br />\n<br />\n在被問及今年的E3發布會上「哪部作品最讓你期待」時，吉田修平回答是《魔物獵人：世界》，他稱讚CAPCOM很擅長開發有趣、可玩性高的動作類游戲。而Sony自家工作室的作品中，他最期待的則是《蜘蛛俠》，吉田表示，這款作品是自由度相當高的開放世界遊戲，每個場景都有多種玩法，例如在發布會上展示的追擊直升機場景，玩家就可以選擇截然不同的路線解決相關事件，在遊玩時，玩家們一定會為這款遊戲的開放性而驚嘆不已。<br />\n<br />\n看來更多的大餅可能要等到今年稍晚些時候的TGS 2017和PSX上才能見到了，我們還是耐心等待吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkgnews.com/41226/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgnews.com%2F41226%2F&d=HM8LQO%2Fvgatu%2FKS7ZQBz8TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2d5be71a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkgnews.com/41226/</a>"},{"pid":"70022925d2524cb772b62dfc5c028d6451da5309","tid":286732,"uid":47823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T00:23:31.000Z","msg":"2019年嘅game留返2018 E3先公佈啦"},{"pid":"58506dac7713e87a95ebe66cd052aa89b07653d9","tid":286732,"uid":69439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"FF7 Remake將成為PS5首輪獨佔遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10db0210a528d96aafe55fc0f9806d034dd17919","tid":286732,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"Tgs"},{"pid":"8d78cd82c587a2ee084ca215ae50f60b6cfee7a2","tid":286732,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"偷人篇訪問，link又唔落"},{"pid":"6d8efb6643797dd8bac10281a6f1fa93f76a7de7","tid":286732,"uid":69439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>偷人篇訪問，link又唔落</blockquote><br />\n近視又加深了！"},{"pid":"c49e244cfb6273eb2eae10d1f828f21e848270cb","tid":286732,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>偷人篇訪問，link又唔落</blockquote><br />\n近視又加深了！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d1beee0b4172cae6fcf17f6ef39d2466c620cf","tid":286732,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>偷人篇訪問，link又唔落</blockquote><br />\n近視又加深了！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講佢個網站，佢貼過黎都係宣傳自己個網咋嘛，有咩問題"},{"pid":"594d1e7ba713261222bde38fdb2113a95d0c67b4","tid":286732,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"2004年公佈會係PS3出<br />\n2017年先出係PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFF7 Remake 2015年公佈<br />\n前排先大批請人開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDeep Down 2013年公佈<br />\n走數到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一向習慣大膽預先N年前公佈定大作<br />\n之後延期再延期或爛尾<br />\n同特區政府大白象工程有得fight<br />\n依家話留力未公佈住<br />\n唔知係咪作風保守左<br />\n定係策略黎要留前鬥後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731400607f3cef5be2ada804757fa88ffb78a670","tid":286732,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB